Feature: User Login and Order Product # features/login.feature:1

  Scenario: Successful Login                                                                                    # features/login.feature:3
    Given I am on the Demo Login Page                                                                           # features/steps/step_definitions.py:22
    When I fill the account information for account StandardUser into the Username field and the Password field # features/steps/step_definitions.py:27
    And I click the Login Button                                                                                # features/steps/step_definitions.py:34
    Then I am redirected to the Demo Main Page                                                                  # features/steps/step_definitions.py:39
    And I verify the App Logo exists                                                                            # features/steps/step_definitions.py:49

  Scenario: Failed Login                                                                                         # features/login.feature:10
    Given I am on the Sauce Demo Login Page                                                                      # features/steps/step_definitions.py:55
    When I fill the account information for account LockedOutUser into the Username field and the Password field # features/steps/step_definitions.py:60
    And I click the Login Button                                                                                 # features/steps/step_definitions.py:34
    Then I verify the Error Message contains the text "Sorry, this user has been banned."                        # features/steps/step_definitions.py:67

  Scenario: Order a product                                                                 # features/login.feature:16
    Given I am on the inventory page                                                        # features/steps/step_definitions.py:74
    When user sorts products from low price to high price                                   # features/steps/step_definitions.py:88
    And user adds lowest priced product                                                     # features/steps/step_definitions.py:95
    And user clicks on cart                                                                 # features/steps/step_definitions.py:100
    And user clicks on checkout                                                             # features/steps/step_definitions.py:106
    And user enters first name John                                                         # features/steps/step_definitions.py:114
    And user enters last name Doe                                                           # features/steps/step_definitions.py:119
    And user enters zip code 123                                                            # features/steps/step_definitions.py:124
    And user clicks Continue button                                                         # features/steps/step_definitions.py:129
    Then I verify in Checkout overview page if the total amount for the added item is $8.63 # features/steps/step_definitions.py:134
    When user clicks Finish button                                                          # features/steps/step_definitions.py:142
    Then Thank You header is shown in Checkout Complete page                                # features/steps/step_definitions.py:149

